''//Cunning//'' is a character's mental ability at rapid and accurate computation and memory retrieval. Cunning is not a good indicator of what a character knows, but is instead indicates how quickly the character is capable of figuring things out, learning new things and how rapidly and accurately the character is able to recall information. 